replies.bodyText:
I thought I had seen some explicit discussion about this idiom, whereby code would need to be migrated to using a Lock, a better monitor, or at least
final Object lock = Object.newIdentityObject();
// ..
synchronized (lock) {
    // …
}
but maybe I am reading more into it than was really there.

